{"tid":270054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好悲慘】「愛滋女」受盡歧視12年 點知原來係誤診","createTime":"2017-06-04T05:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T06:03:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6abed140158de628b5b4e66e68e8f6fb8c2db860","tid":270054,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:38:26.000Z","msg":"即時國際  2017-06-03 20:31:40 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n泰國一名女子自8歲起驗出患愛滋病，受盡12年歧視眼光，當她長大後再作一次愛滋病測試，竟呈陰性反應，原來一直以來都是受誤診所累。<br />\n<br />\n20歲的沙恩素邁（Suthida Saengsumat）由於父親死於愛滋、母親亦疑受感染，所以她8歲時被老師安排作愛滋病測試，結果呈陽性反應，但未有作二次測試去確認。她自此在受歧視的環境下長大，同學、鄰居全都避開她，令她終受不了而停學，亦放棄了讀醫夢想。<br />\n<br />\n她稱結婚後雖有避孕，但仍然懷孕，如今育有分別5歲及1歲的孩子。當幼子的愛滋病測試呈陰性反應時，她在過去周二決定再接受測試，結果竟同是陰性，於是暫停服用愛滋病藥物。由於她對健康仍有疑慮，於是在周四再作一次檢驗確認結果，並證實並非愛滋病帶菌者。<br />\n<br />\n醫生表示現今的愛滋病測試比起過去更為準確，失誤率約為千分之一，所以足證沙恩素邁是誤診。醫療團隊亦正了解沙恩素邁自小服食愛滋病藥物多年，是否對健康有任何副作用。"},{"pid":"9e85ea5da1217763916063fde56e28ef80148ea7","tid":270054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170603&amp;guid=56777991&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170603%26guid%3D56777991%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=FWGQGMRI8%2BR9BXZI3Qvkef%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5cb68579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170603%26guid%3D56777991%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=90e38e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170603&amp;guid=56777991&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"6cd0b76b6b9add6e134bcbfb39742cb47962273f","tid":270054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362b7a6c5048185f095b5c38e773d43fe0769ce9","tid":270054,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"有愛滋都有人埋單？"},{"pid":"f35fc62811806bbfb389d51bd71fdbba2f4e8b8e","tid":270054,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"點解佢以為有愛滋嗰時仲要生仔 而唔落咗佢"},{"pid":"99f7e664114c216fe8365ef0f21aae58a90cdcb4","tid":270054,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有愛滋都有人埋單？</blockquote><br />\n真愛..."},{"pid":"b8b699bd267c1915cfc109738a2fbcdd8449b700","tid":270054,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"如果係美國呢單野有排賠"},{"pid":"8914ec58fa1d4d11002053ee8675a6debd97b33a","tid":270054,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"20歲有個5歲仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfbi?"},{"pid":"6391c5894ce3e46e1568bf8f44e535e913f4bece","tid":270054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20歲有個5歲仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfbi?</blockquote><br />\n人工受精"}]}